{"type": "article", "id": 7055, "title": "Axor Starck V 水龙头", "description": "", "date": "2015-03-04T07:17:48Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606143629O9d2lFwDUqW56ceB.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"white-space:normal;\">法国设计师 Philippe Starck 带来这件作品是为德国卫浴品牌 Hansgrohe 设计的一款水龙头，水龙头的外观透明，因此可以清晰看见水流在水龙头中的流动状态。同时，玻璃的通透性使得一旦有异物出现，便会在水龙头内壁暴露无遗。水龙头上部的可拆卸性方便了清洁，你甚至可以把它拆下来放进洗碗机里面洗洗呢。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"white-space:normal;\">\r\n\t<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143627jlviHf0zbQgLqWnC.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"0.56388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n\t</p>\r\n\t<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143627tBE1TF3svVJK9rmY.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"0.56388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n\t</p>\r\n\t<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143628t98RrpVAZSmOwe7j.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"0.56388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n\t</p>\r\n\t<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143628L7iZUTOxVEavdSDf.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"0.61296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n\t</p>\r\n\t<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t\t<br>\r\n\t</p>\r\n<br>\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}